  "description": "This is a addon for the Origins mod.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod adds one new origin: The Deviling!&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">PS: This mod requires the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/origins\">Origins</a> mod to work.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Deviling has a netherrack as an icon in the selection menu.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Description:&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">As a deviling you gain the ability to fly. You take slightly less damage and you need access to the nether or end dimension to survive.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abilities:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li>Nether Burn</li>\n<li>Gift of Flight</li>\n<li>Launch</li>\n<li>Eyes of the Devil</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/uy9QFaQWR7\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_DISCORD.png\" alt=\"discord\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Discord server:&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/uy9QFaQWR7\">https://discord.gg/uy9QFaQWR7</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_PROMO.png\" alt=\"hosting\"/></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Want to host your own server?&nbsp; &nbsp; Use code: CHILLZONE for 25% off your first month!&nbsp;<br /><strong><em><a class=\"anchor-3Z-8Bb anchorUnderlineOnHover-2ESHQB\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\" role=\"button\" href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone</a>&nbsp;</em></strong></p>",
